have seriously affected the outcome of the caucuses in the
Bremerton area,'' all 10 members of the Washington state delegation
said in a letter to Sen. John Glenn, D-Ohio, chairman of the Senate
Governmental Affairs Committee.
   The committee is currently considering changes in the Hatch Act.
