fiance she has never dated.
   ``Everything looks so small, so different from here,'' Miss
Sanders, 19, said Thursday after a fire truck's bucket brought her
down from the three-story-high shack where she spent 517 days with
her feline companion, Pole Cat.
   ``My knees are wobbly but I feel great,'' said Miss Sanders, who
was embraced by her mother, Mauri Rose Sanders.
