<1ST_LINE>u f AM-Koppers 2ndLd-Writethru   03-25 0832</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Koppers, 2nd Ld-Writethru,0858</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Retransmitting</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 12th graf to CLARIFY Pennsylvania ad ran in more papers</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By MARIANN CAPRINO</BYLINE>
